# NOTE: This file is symlinked to ~/.gitignore and used as the global
# core.excludesfile, so it must only contain patterns safe to apply to every
# repository. APM dependencies and generated artifacts (CLAUDE.md, AGENTS.md,
# apm_modules/, .cursor/, .claude/skills/, etc.) are dotfiles-repo specific and
# would wrongly hide those files in other repos, so they live in this repo's
# local .git/info/exclude instead (recreated by install.sh).
